{"tid":1125170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京出席「一帶一路」峰會　昂山素姬：中國是緬甸的榜樣","createTime":"2019-04-25T13:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T13:48:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"104ba142b7b4837cbf42e6b2c4a7eddbefa678d6","tid":1125170,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/25/214621_eca379d72d1d83c586c755b2d5c5d883.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2F214621_eca379d72d1d83c586c755b2d5c5d883.png&h=8797fcfe&s={SIZE}\" />緬甸國務資政昂山素姬昨日抵達北京首都機場，參加中國舉辦的第2屆「一帶一路」峰會。陸媒《新京報》、澎湃新聞等引述昂山素姬在論壇上指出，中國是緬甸一個榜樣，證明了有決心、有了努力與勤奮最後能夠得到什麼，世界上沒有任何一個國家在勤奮這點上能夠超越中國。<br />\n<br />\n昂山素姬表示，今次是帶着友誼而來，沒有相互信任和理解，就不會有真正的友誼與合作，希望在相互信任和理解的基礎之上建立合作和友誼的關係，而不是一種以影響力和權力為基礎的合作。<br />\n<br />\n在昂山素姬訪華前夕，3,000多名緬甸民眾周一（22日）在緬甸北部示威，抗議政府打算恢復中國支持興建的密松大壩工程，抗議者批評大壩工程會造成巨大環境損害，對緬甸沒有好處。<br />\n<br />\n昂山素姬任國務資政以來，緬甸國內人權狀況受到關注。國際特赦組織（Amnesty International）因緬甸國務資政昂山素姬對軍方逼害羅興亞穆斯林「漠不關心」，決定褫奪昂山素姬的良心大使。<br />\n<br />\n2名路透社記者Wa Lone和Kyaw Soe Oo，年前調查羅興亞人道危機時被捕，被緬甸法院以違反「官方機密法」定罪，判監7年。昂山素姬去年出席越南河內舉行的世界經濟論壇時表示，緬甸法院判詞清楚說明，對於2名路透社記者被判監，是因為他們干犯了殖民時期的「官方機密法」，與言論自由無關<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83-%E6%98%82%E5%B1%B1%E7%B4%A0%E5%A7%AC-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%AF%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%9C%E6%A8%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2598%2582%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E5%25A7%25AC-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A6%259C%25E6%25A8%25A3%2F&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=3658bb8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2598%2582%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E5%25A7%25AC-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A6%259C%25E6%25A8%25A3%2F&h=c10b7086\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83-%E6%98%82%E5%B1%B1%E7%B4%A0%E5%A7%AC-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%AF%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%9C%E6%A8%A3/</a>"},{"pid":"b9c3624ab892e2855418f41ec376dd361d4ae519","tid":1125170,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"奶共素雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}